{"tid":1146581,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"笑撚死人，見到篇文話藝人無錯喎！","createTime":"2019-05-09T10:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T10:22:33.000Z","uid":242482,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aee79698280b8b406f2fe5ce8191721b8a278632","tid":1146581,"uid":242482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:10:05.000Z","msg":"見到篇膠文同大家Share吓<br />\n笑到我腸都跌埋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dvblob.blob.core.windows.net/dvblob//Content/Upload/Charts/ReplaceImages/2019-05/fefc5fa4-3820-4d5b-bf89-e88e5c7a2d9a_re.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdvblob.blob.core.windows.net%2Fdvblob%2F%2FContent%2FUpload%2FCharts%2FReplaceImages%2F2019-05%2Ffefc5fa4-3820-4d5b-bf89-e88e5c7a2d9a_re.png&h=10676b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 1 劉德華填海論<br />\n<br />\n唔好因為一個意見，否定半世誠懇勤勉<br />\n<br />\n劉德華一直嘅形象都好好，好到有「民間特首」嘅稱號，喺香港，「劉華」仲更係勤奮努力嘅代名詞。但喺上年年尾，劉德華義務幫團結香港基金嘅《讓下一代看見》做旁白，出聲撐東大嶼填海計畫，俾人狂數咩都唔識亂咁講，聲名一夜間變到好不堪。其實大家立場可以唔同，但唔應該因為咁而否定優秀人格，一單還一單，劉德華喺好多方面都係一個榜樣。<br />\n<br />\n 2 鄭欣宜身形受攻擊<br />\n<br />\n不要低頭，光環會掉下來<br />\n<br />\n鄭欣宜咁多年嚟，都冇咩觀眾緣，成日俾人喺網上奚落，仲攞佢身型嚟做攻擊武器，人哋女仔嚟㗎，你估真係可以唔介意咩。當成個香港都拎佢變肥變瘦嚟做新聞，你諗吓個壓力可以幾大喇！好彩欣宜諗通咗，唔再在意唔友善嘅目光、言論，就好似佢首《女神》嘅歌詞：「人類看不起，我都好看。」放低標準審美觀嘅壓力，勇敢做自己，為自己而活。<br />\n<br />\n入面仲有好多膠人膠事<br />\n大家無聊入去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://dailyview.tw/hk/Daily/2019/05/06\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdailyview.tw%2Fhk%2FDaily%2F2019%2F05%2F06&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=cac3122a\" target=\"_blank\">https://dailyview.tw/hk/Daily/2019/05/06</a>"},{"pid":"dce800c841714e3b1ebec3c667f8ffd2db2955b9","tid":1146581,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r